description:
I've teamed up with Pause and Beef once again, this time we are taking on Simulation Protocol #1 (Animosity), a CTM map by TikaroHD. The goal is to find all 16 wool colors and place these on the victory monument to finish the map.

PauseUnpause: http://www.youtube.com/PauseUnpause
VintageBeef: http://www.youtube.com/user/VintageBeef

Map By: TikaroHD
Map Download: http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1978705-ctm-collection-simulation-protocol-series-by-tikarohd/page__hl__ctm
